  "title": "Sales Support Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle overseas existing and new customers</p></li><li><p>Follow up customers enquires</p></li><li><p>Provide quotations to customers</p></li><li><p>Follow up with overseas existing customers for repeat orders/ promote related products</p></li><li><p>Issue sales order</p></li><li><p>Assist Vietnam Branch (SSBVN, SIGVN) – RFQ, sales and direct import</p></li><li><p>Sales order (overseas)</p></li><li><p>Customer Evaluation</p></li><li><p>Overseas trip forecast report</p></li><li><p>Sales meeting agenda & minutes</p></li><li><p>Sales personnel weekly report</p></li><li><p>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Preferable candidate possess at least Degree/Diploma in any fields</p></li><li><p>Strong interpersonal skills and ability to build relationships</p></li><li><p>Knowledge SAP is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and effectively manage multiple priorities.</p></li><li><p>Monday to Friday, 8:30am to 6:30pm</p></li><li><p><em><strong>Singaporean only may apply</strong></em></p></li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><p>Annual Wage Supplement (AWS)</p></li><li><p>Variable Bonus</p></li><li><p>Outpatient medical </p></li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
